# Tailwind

- Use Tailwind CSS for styling; avoid vanilla CSS in `<style>` blocks
- Do **not** use `space-y-*` or `space-x-*`; use flex or grid with `gap-*` instead
- Avoid arbitrary values when an existing utlity class is close to the value desired
- Always use the semantic color system, with light-dark values
- Do **not** introduce new colors that don't adhere to the light-dark system
- Always attempt to use AdminButton.svelte for any new button in the /admin route, choose the closest variant
- Always attempt to use AdminCard.svelte for any bordered container in the /admin route, choose the closest variant
